        of First Congregational Church in Washington, DC, and would spend the next 23 years there.
        While visiting the Himalayas in 2007, John fell ill and spent several weeks in the hospital.
        He died in his home, surrounded by his family, on January 15th, 2008. This collection
        contains materials both personal and profession from across John's life. Included are
        sermons, columns in Gabriel's Horn titled "A View from Here", other collected writings on
